'''Chief Military Prosecutor Office''' ({{lang-pl|Naczelna Prokuratura Wojskowa}}) is the highest organizational unit in [[Poland]]'s military's [[Lawyer|attorney]]'s office. It's directed by Chief Military Prosecutor (''Naczelny Prokurator Wojskowy''). The office was created in 1919. Current Chief Military Prosecutor is [[Tomasz Szałek]].

